text:
Come here on Monday evenings and join the residents working out. Circuit trainings with kettle bells provided.

On other days, good place for pull ups and sit up

Great and quiet park besides the construction on a building nice and peaceful park!
If you live on Chiltern drive come and visit this place for a workout or just hangout and play Badminton or Table Tennis.
A quiet place for exercise. The equipment has just been renovated and quite new.
Few things for young kids to use in the park
